name: プロデューサー
trans: You did great out there, Yuika.

name: 結華
text:
──うん！
ありがとう、プロデューサー！

name: プロデューサー
text: ──……やっぱり結華のステージはすごいな
trans:
──...I knew you were going to do great,
but your performance out there really
blew me away!

name: プロデューサー
text:
楽しくて、かっこよくて、クールで、可愛くて、綺麗で
──いろんな結華を前に、目が離せなくなるんだ
trans:
It was fun, hype, cool, cute, beautiful──
every single thing about you was out there.
And I couldn't take my eyes off of you!

name: プロデューサー
text: そうなるように、結華がずっと頑張ってきたから
trans: All that blood, sweat, and tears paid off, Yuika.

name: 結華
text:
かっこつけたいって言った手前、
それぐらいはやんなきゃだからね
trans:
I told you earlier that I wanted to show off,
didn't I? I had to at least give thaaat much!

name: 結華
text: 最初のファンからお墨付きをもらえて、何より！
trans:
What mattered the most was earning the
seal of approval from my very first fan!
